            <h1>Gadget Repository</h1>
            <p>The Gadget Repository enables gadget server administrators to manage portal gadgets.
                The administrators can add new gadgets, modify them and make default gadgets for newly registered users.'Add new gadgets' can be done in four ways.<br/>
		<li>Using gadget URL-This option can be used to add a gadget from a http gadget repository location where the gadget stored.</li>
		<li>Using gadget file path-This option can be used to add a gadget by uploading its xml file.</li>
		<li>Using gadget zip file path-This option can be used to add a gadget by uploading it as a zip file.</li>
		<li>Using gadget registry path-This option can be used to add a gadget from registry by browsing registry and selecting the required gadget.</li>
 
            </p>
